quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  6,53,"Ko wano non min njarribornoo yoga maɓɓe yoga, fii yo ɓe mbi'u : "E ko ɓee ɗoo Alla Neemini(dokke)dow mu'en hakkunde amen?" E Alla wonaali ɓurɗo Anndude yettooɓe [Mo] ɓen?"
  6,54,"Si arii e maa ɓeen gooŋɗinayɓe Aayeeje Amen ɗe, maaku : "Yo kisal won e mo'on! Joomi mon Waɗɗinii e Makko yurmeende nden : wonnde kala golluɗo e mo'on bone hara ko e majjere, refti o tuubi ɓaawo ɗuum o moƴƴini, haray ko o kafroowo, jurmotooɗo."
  6,55,"Ko wano non min paccitirta Aayeeje ɗeen, fii no laawol bon ɓe ɓe feeñira."
  6,56,"Maaku : "Min mi haɗaama nde mi rewata ɓeen ɓe noddoton gah Alla". Maaku : "Mi jokkataa beleeɗe mon ɗen : gooŋɗii haray mi majjii, haray kadi mi wonaani e feewɓe ɓeen"."
  6,57,"Maaku : "Min miɗo e ɓanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, on njeddi ɗum. Mi alaa ko kawjanton kon. Ñaawoore nden ko Alla woodani : Himo Fillo goonga, ko Kaŋko ɓuri moƴƴude e fensitooɓe (seerndooɓe)goona e fenaande."
  6,58,"Maaku : "Sinno miɗo joginoo kon ko kawjiratnoɗon, fiyaaku on gasayno hakkunde am e mo'on". Ko Alla ɓuri Anndude tooñooɓe ɓeen."
  6,59,"Ko kañum jogi coktirɗe ko wirnii, anndaa ɗum si wanaa Kaŋko. Homo Anndi ko woni ka jeeri e ka maayo. Kaakol yanataa si wanaa hara homo Anndi fii maggol, wanaa abbere ka niɓe leydi, wanaa keccol wanaa joorungol, si wanaa no e deftere ɓanngunde. (Feeñnde)."